      "message": "Abandoned\n\nPatch is wrong since cpt is a local thing and must be defined when using lnet_res_[un]lock(cpt). Change-Id: Ifbc6573664fdc4849b9155b6102c8589e692996b\nin Gerrit change at http://review.whamcloud.com/17840/\nseems to be a much better direction to fix LU-7824 problem.",
