        "committer": {
          "name": "Bruno Faccini",
          "email": "bruno.faccini@intel.com",
          "date": "2016-01-06 18:26:38.000000000",
          "tz": 60
        },
        "subject": "LU-7324 lnet: avoid race on ptl_msg_[stealing,delayed] lists",
        "message": "LU-7324 lnet: avoid race on ptl_msg_[stealing,delayed] lists\n\nCrashes have been encountered in lnet_ptl_match_delay() where a\nthread expects to retrieve a lnet_msg it has linked on one of the\nptl_msg_[stealing,delayed] lists, when he lnet_msg has already\nbeen unlinked and even freed by some other thread.\nTo prevent this keep [res,ptl]_locks during the whole for loop.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly testgroup=review\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie5a203afb09c2b913490bb2d6c0979b0e57c4f11\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
